data.description: Incredible, maintenance free living in this 1684 SqFt ree-standing ranch home built in 2021 & situated on the 11th Hole of Quail Hollow. This home is loaded w/over $60K in upgrades. Fantastic open floor plan with a Huge Gourmet Eat-in Kitchen Boasting QuRtx countertops a large center island w/breakfast bar, SS Appliances, Subway style ceramic tile backsplash & built in counter top range with Hood! The kitchen opens to a nice dining room that walks out to a covered porch overlooking pond and the golf course! Open Great room with Marble Gas FP. Owners Suite features a trayed ceiling in the bedroom & a glamorous bathroom equipped with a double sinks w/quartz c-tops, ceramic tile shower w/custom glass door & large walk-in closet! 2 additional bedrooms 1 of which has French doors & is currently being used as an office!
